Then I emailed the city traffic engineer who told me that no report or study had been done and that I was misinformed.

270
00:22:44,813 --> 00:22:55,699
So I don't think that the traffic commission has any right to sign off on this temporary measure until a full traffic engineering report is completed.

271
00:22:56,740 --> 00:23:03,564
What would you expect that, just for clarification, you're looking for a traffic study to determine what?

272
00:23:03,944 --> 00:23:04,765
The number of accidents?

273
00:23:06,298 --> 00:23:13,000
to determine the traffic patterns, to determine design alternatives.

274
00:23:15,521 --> 00:23:15,821
Sorry?

275
00:23:16,322 --> 00:23:18,242
We have an established traffic pattern.

276
00:23:18,642 --> 00:23:21,523
We're just eliminating one of those patterns.

277
00:23:23,224 --> 00:23:30,787
So when you remove the opportunity for left turns there, you are increasing the speed of traffic on Main Street.

278
00:23:31,407 --> 00:23:33,708
And yes, there are fewer accidents

279
