I was someone who commuted on the 354 in Medford Square.

282
00:23:49,712 --> 00:23:53,313
I had to cross that intersection twice, twice daily.

283
00:23:54,594 --> 00:23:57,455
Now it is twice as difficult.

284
00:23:59,585 --> 00:24:04,047
I do not think this is a net increase in public safety.

285
00:24:04,487 --> 00:24:10,329
I think this is a net decrease in automobile accidents.

286
00:24:11,409 --> 00:24:25,754
However, you are making the community less walkable and you're making the people who live in the neighborhood adjacent to Medford Square feel disentitled and less safe.

287
00:24:27,237 --> 00:24:29,557
Okay.

288
00:24:29,797 --> 00:24:30,698
Could I ask a question?

289
00:24:30,718 --> 00:24:33,758
I don't understand one of the comments.

290
00:24:33,818 --> 00:24:35,278
