291
00:24:35,298 --> 00:24:51,861
Sorry, legitimately, you said this makes it less walkable, and I don't understand that because it looks to me, and I have to judge in this, that it makes it easier to walk because there'll be fewer cars to contend with.

292
00:24:51,881 --> 00:24:54,202
