293
00:24:54,922 --> 00:24:56,202
The turning cars,

294
00:24:57,142 --> 00:25:01,463
allow for pedestrians to be blocked from main street traffic.

295
00:25:02,204 --> 00:25:03,024
They work together.

296
00:25:06,585 --> 00:25:09,666
The turning cars slow down the speed of traffic on main street.

297
00:25:13,067 --> 00:25:13,467
Okay.

298
00:25:13,928 --> 00:25:20,970
It seems that happens at rush hour times, which I would like studied in the traffic report.

299
00:25:23,281 --> 00:25:27,083
And that is also when people are walking across this intersection more.

300
00:25:27,783 --> 00:25:29,704
There is a symbiotic relationship.

301
