I gave him several suggestions.

303
00:25:40,822 --> 00:25:46,648
I have been asking for years for a wholesale redesign from Salem Street to Mystic.

304
00:25:47,729 --> 00:25:53,795
And this call is the first time I've heard of any plans of a redesign of this intersection.

305
00:25:53,815 --> 00:25:58,180
This is the first time I've heard of any plans of a new fire department building.

306
00:25:58,960 --> 00:26:00,122
Was that just announced right now?

307
00:26:02,343 --> 00:26:03,624
know.

308
00:26:04,185 --> 00:26:18,354
Chief, I'm going to post the information for the city alerts to sign up for that because that's where there's often information about the public meetings and stuff that's going on if residents aren't aware of things that are happening in the city.

309
00:26:18,874 --> 00:26:26,099
Yeah, none of what we spoke about about the redesign of that roadway or the fire station is new information.

310
00:26:26,139 --> 00:26:28,881
It's been out in public for quite some time.

311
00:26:29,894 --> 00:26:35,897
If not, several years on them on the main street, mystic intersection.

312
00:26:36,658 --> 00:26:46,343
Okay, well, I think you should do a traffic engineering report ahead of that design and come up with a design solution for this intersection.

313
00:26:47,144 --> 00:26:52,867
And then another permanent design solution for after the redesign.

314
00:26:56,245 --> 00:26:59,546
I don't think an undesigned solution is the right measure here.

315
00:27:00,067 --> 00:27:05,269
And I don't think a solution without engineering is right.

316
00:27:06,949 --> 00:27:08,130
And I'll cede my time.

317
00:27:09,281 --> 00:27:26,403
Chief, maybe if Tim or I want to speak to the fact that there is a major MassDOT project to redesign this entire area and I will try and find on our web page where we have information about that that is involving a lot of traffic

318
00:27:26,523 --> 00:27:30,745
It is a very complicated, difficult location and area.

319
00:27:30,906 --> 00:27:32,807
All of this is being taken into account.

320
00:27:33,247 --> 00:27:35,228
There have been public meetings about it.

321
00:27:35,288 --> 00:27:37,709
I expect there'll be more public meetings in the future.

322
00:27:37,729 --> 00:27:40,271
We're waiting for the next iteration of designs.

323
00:27:42,252 --> 00:27:52,618
And as I understand it, this is a temporary safety measure until we have a full redesign from Medford Square to the intersection at Main and Mystic.

324
00:27:56,203 --> 00:27:56,563
Excellent.

325
00:27:56,603 --> 00:28:02,546
If you could post that, and we'll try to get that out to everyone in this area over the next couple of days.

326
00:28:03,747 --> 00:28:05,307
Go ahead, Sergeant.

