00:28:22,670 --> 00:28:29,754
I just want to jump in first because you mentioned how South Street is safer now.

335
00:28:29,834 --> 00:28:32,135
Maybe safer, not safe.

336
00:28:33,156 --> 00:28:38,018
I spent the afternoon going through dispatch logs for this year and last year.

337
00:28:39,839 --> 00:28:44,362
Now, October was a bad month for Emerson and Maine.

338
00:28:44,622 --> 00:28:45,222
I'll give you that.

339
00:28:45,262 --> 00:28:46,083
You had a bad day.

340
00:28:47,340 --> 00:28:53,343
There's also been at least one accident since you've done what you've done to the street.

