00:28:54,003 --> 00:28:57,304
There's been another MVA, at least one on dispatch.

342
00:28:57,884 --> 00:29:09,909
I don't know, your numbers seem inflated according to what I'm going to state now, but in October, there were 126 reported MVAs in Medford.

343
00:29:11,230 --> 00:29:16,172
27 of them involved Main Street at some intersection of Main Street and another street.

344
00:29:17,683 --> 00:29:23,026
There were four that occurred at Emerson, and I'll give you that, it was a busy month for Emerson.

345
00:29:24,286 --> 00:29:30,929
There were three at Royal Street, there were two at South Street, and there were one at 7-Eleven in Main Street.

346
00:29:32,530 --> 00:29:39,813
This year so far, you have 14 MVAs on the log for South Street.

347
00:29:41,554 --> 00:29:45,996
You have seven for the year from Emerson Street.

348
00:29:46,597 --> 00:29:47,257
Last year,

349
00:29:49,155 --> 00:29:52,477
There were only two for the year at Emerson Street in Maine.

350
00:29:53,338 --> 00:30:00,724
And there were 12 for South Street in Maine last year.

351
00:30:03,646 --> 00:30:06,988
Now, I'll echo what everyone else in the neighborhood has said.

352
00:30:07,028 --> 00:30:09,530
You have about 80 plus homes back there.

353
00:30:10,171 --> 00:30:11,472
You have two ways in.

