00:30:18,360 --> 00:30:27,983
And as the other tenant said, one access to that 93 Route 16 ramp has been already taken away with South Street.

357
00:30:28,563 --> 00:30:30,844
And now this one is further taken away.

358
00:30:30,964 --> 00:30:43,288
