363
00:31:20,887 --> 00:31:21,988
And this is what's happening.

364
00:31:22,088 --> 00:31:37,520
And also another thing is is that when you pull out of Emerson Street to take a left, you have delivery trucks in front of 200 Main Street, large vans, and you have a bus stop there.

365
00:31:38,140 --> 00:31:39,581
That's a huge blind spot.

366
00:31:39,681 --> 00:31:44,505
No one can see anyone coming out, not even a pedestrian stepping out onto the crosswalk.

367
00:31:45,668 --> 00:32:02,203
And when the right lane slows down for the pedestrian or the outcoming traffic, the people in the left lane scoot out and go around, and they just think, oh, someone's stopping for something else, and I'm just going to go around them.

368
00:32:02,323 --> 00:32:09,709
And that's when someone's going to step out in front of a car that's letting them cross the street, and they're going to get hurt or killed.

369
00:32:10,350 --> 00:32:12,252
And then you'll pay attention.

370
00:32:13,564 --> 00:32:16,145
and see that it's not just a four-wheel problem.

371
00:32:16,545 --> 00:32:18,886
We have a two-wheel problem, a foot problem.

372
00:32:19,446 --> 00:32:21,166
We have a lot of problems.

373
00:32:21,226 --> 00:32:32,510
I'm not saying that that intersection is no worse, is worse than any other, but you have problems throughout the city, especially along Main Street and Mystic Avenue.

374
00:32:34,490 --> 00:32:36,091
It's the influx of cars.

375
00:32:36,911 --> 00:32:40,272
It's the discourteous drivers during peak times of the day.

376
00:32:42,188 --> 00:32:50,853
