00:36:31,085 --> 00:36:31,285
No.

426
00:36:31,585 --> 00:36:38,990
Again, it's not to make this a permanent solution.

427
00:36:39,150 --> 00:36:40,831
Let's make it a safe solution.

428
00:36:40,891 --> 00:36:45,073
And I understand the opinions of what would be safer, what not would be safer.

429
00:36:45,093 --> 00:36:49,136
But in our experience, this is what we do.

430
00:36:50,875 --> 00:36:57,517
including the traffic engineer's input, this would be the safest, most immediate action to take.

431
00:36:57,817 --> 00:37:11,201
And we did take into consideration the inconvenience to the residents, but there is avenues, and I'm repeating myself, I don't mean to sort of distress this, but I just, it's an attempt to answer some of those questions.

